\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
One a single out-of-sample 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\mathbf{x},y\right)$
\end_inset

, the error is 
\begin_inset Formula $e\left(h\left(\mathbf{x}\right),y\right)$
\end_inset

.
